    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mmob1",
      "speakerName": "カメラマン",
      "speakerNameEn": "Photographer",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mmob1.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "はい、以上で撮影終了です！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Alright‚ the shoot is finished!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mmob1",
      "speakerName": "カメラマン",
      "speakerNameEn": "Photographer",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mmob1.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "お疲れ様でしたー！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Great job‚ all of you!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.7333333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "一同",
      "speakerNameEn": "Everyone",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ありがとうございました！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you so much!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.366666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "01-2d",
      "startTime": 8.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_09/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_09-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん\n撮影、どうでしたか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san!\nwhat do you think of the shoot?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_09/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_09-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "ああ……みんなちゃんと可愛く撮れていたと思う",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I think everyone looked cute in the photos.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.125859827744332,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "01-2d",
      "startTime": 15.959193161077698
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_09/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_09-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "それなら良かったです\nアイドルとしての写真撮影って、慣れてなかったから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good to hear that.\nI wasn't used to photoshoots as an idol.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.259193161077665,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_09/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_09-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "私も、みんなの輪に馴染めて一安心かも\nきっと同世代に見えるよね？ ……ね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m relieved I was able to fit in with everyone.\nI’m sure we look around the same age‚ right? …Right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.45919316107766,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "01-2d",
      "startTime": 26.459193161077703
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "01-2d",
      "startTime": 31.015949966806843
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_09/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_09-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そうですね\n安心して大丈夫だと思いますよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "W-well… I guess.\nI don’t think you have anything to worry about.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.382616633473546,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "01-2d",
      "startTime": 36.08261663347355
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_09/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_09-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "……あの、{user}さん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Hey‚ {user}-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.08261663347355,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_09/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_09-szk002.m4a",
      "text": "私達、どうでしたか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "How did we do?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.032616681157265,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "01-2d",
      "startTime": 42.147582596837225
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "01-2d",
      "startTime": 44.91424926350382
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_09/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_09-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "（課題点は正直に言った方がいいよな）\n（ 変に気を遣っても、彼女達のためにならないし）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（I should give them my honest feedback.）\n（It won’t benefit them if I beat around the bush.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.914249263503855,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "01-2d",
      "startTime": 49.117145381667896
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_09/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_09-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "アイドルらしく可愛く撮れてたよ。ただ……\n写真越しにも伝わる明るさが、あと少し欲しかったな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Your photos were really cute and idol-like‚ but…\nI wish they conveyed a bit more of your cheerfulness.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.35047871500125,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "01-2d",
      "startTime": 56.90020159843765
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_09/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_09-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "雫も……ポージングは完璧だった\nでも笑い方はもうちょっと特訓が必要だな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Shizuku… your poses were perfect‚\nbut you’ll need to practice your smile a little more.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.033534931771015,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "01-2d",
      "startTime": 63.366868265104344
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_09/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_09-szk003.m4a",
      "text": "そう、ですか。わかりました……\nもうちょっと……頑張ってみます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see. Okay…\nI’ll try… a little harder.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.56686826510435,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "01-2d",
      "startTime": 71.76686826510435
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_09/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_09-chs003.m4a",
      "text": "雫ちゃん……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Shizuku-chan…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.76686826510435,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "01-2d",
      "startTime": 74.00020159843764
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_09/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_09-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "でも、慣れない中でみんなよく頑張ったよ\n今日はもう帰ってゆっくり休もう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Still‚ all of you did a great job‚ despite your lack of experience.\nLet’s head back‚ so you can all rest.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.56686826510436,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "01-2d",
      "startTime": 79.90020159843766
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_09/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_09-hrk003.m4a",
      "text": "そうね\nさ、みんな着替えてこよっか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okay.\nAlright‚ let’s all go get changed.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.3002015984377,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "01-2d",
      "startTime": 85.66686826510436
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_mna-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 86.03353493177106
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_09/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_09-mna001.m4a",
      "text": "今回はちゃんと、言葉選んで言えたね\n{user}も少しは成長したかな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You chose your words carefully this time.\nI guess you’ve matured a little‚ {user}-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.30020159843768,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "01-2d",
      "startTime": 92.73353493177108
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_09/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_09-mna002.m4a",
      "text": "心配しなくても大丈夫だよ\n私、思うんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don’t worry about it.\nYou know what I think?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.60020159843764,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "01-2d",
      "startTime": 97.77285828512008
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_09/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_09-mna003.m4a",
      "text": "きっと、雫ちゃんと千紗ちゃんは……\n二人一緒なら、大丈夫だって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I think Shizuku-chan and Chisa-chan are gonna be just fine\nas long as they’re together.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.33952495178671,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_09/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_09-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "そうは言うけど……根拠は？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah? What makes you so sure?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.9649525978084,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "01-2d",
      "startTime": 106.50910223503041
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_09/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_09-mna004.m4a",
      "text": "あのね……これだけみんなの近くにいるのに\nピンときてないのは、鈍感過ぎると思うよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You see… even though you're so close to everyone here‚\nI think it's because you're too insensitive not to notice.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.64243556836414,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_09/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_09-mna005.m4a",
      "text": "……琴乃とさくらちゃんも、そうだったじゃない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s like what happened with Kotono and Sakura-chan.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.44116952384049,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "01-2d",
      "startTime": 117.30783619050715
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_09/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_09-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "……琴乃と、さくら？\n二人と雫達は、全然違う気がするんだけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "….Kotono and Sakura?\nBut they’re so different from Shizuku and Chisa….",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 119.7745028571738,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "01-2d",
      "startTime": 123.60783619050714
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_09/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_09-mna006.m4a",
      "text": "ヒントはここまで\n答えは自分で見つけたら？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s the only hint you get.\nIt’s up to you to find the answer.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.54116952384054,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_way-00-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "02-3d",
